dct_title_s: New sectional, township & county map of Washington
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures.; Covers also a portion of northern Oregon.; Shows county boundaries, military and Indian reservations, railroads, lighthouses, and stage roads.; "Entered according to act of Congress in the year 1889 ... in the office of the Librarian of Congress at Washington."; Prime meridians: Washington and Greenwich.
